text: Molyobka () is a rural locality (a village) in Asovskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 44 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 1.5 km east from Asovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Molyobka, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
